posting_body: ['Live near the beautiful marina!', 'Parks, Shopping, Entertainment, Restaurants, etc!!', 'In the center of it all!!', 'To schedule a tour', 'Book online at', '<URL>', 'Description', 'Immersed in the heart of the action, our community ensures that residents are never far from their next adventure.', 'Fuel outdoor fun at Marina Park on Lake Washington, spend the day shopping at nearby boutiques or wind down with a much-needed drink or mouthwatering meal at neighborhood restaurants and bars, many of which are just steps away!', 'When it comes to luxury, it’s all in the details.', 'From stainless-steel appliances and brick veneer to glass railings and decorative lighting, our Kirkland apartments go above and beyond to make ordinary routines extraordinary!', 'Details', 'Availability date:', 'Today', 'Pets:', 'Cats, Small Dogs (< 25lb), Large Dogs (> 25lb)', 'Pet notes:', 'Breed restrictions apply, please contact leasing office for details.', 'Deposit:', '$300.00', 'Leasing options:', 'Leasing notes:', 'None', 'Application fee:', '$59', 'Amenities', 'Included in Utilities Cost:', 'NA', 'Utilities Cost:', 'Depends on usage', 'Laundry:', 'In Unit', 'Parking type:', 'Garage, Off-Street', 'Parking notes:', 'Controlled access garage', 'Appliances:', 'Dishwasher, Refrigerator, Microwave, Range/Oven', 'Exterior:', 'Balcony/patio, Deck', 'Heating/cooling:', 'Double pane / Storm windows, Forced air heat', 'Wiring:', 'Cable-ready, High-speed internet, Intercom system', 'Facilities and Recreation:', 'Fitness center, Barbecue, Tennis court', 'Security and Access:', 'Elevator, Security system, Controlled access', 'Views:', 'City, Mountain, Water, Park', 'Additional features:', 'Non-Smoking Property', 'Offered by:', 'Blanton Turner', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
